Package scenario.integrita.historytree

Class NodeAddress

java.lang.Object
scenario.integrita.historytree.NodeAddress
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class NodeAddress extends Object implements Serializable
holds the address of a node of the history tree. position represents the operation number. level indicates at which height of the history tree the node is located. level ranges from 0 to log2(position)+1.
